{"id":8398,"date":"2022-04-26T15:15:08","date_gmt":"2022-04-26T08:15:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?p=8398"},"modified":"2023-05-11T11:19:37","modified_gmt":"2023-05-11T04:19:37","slug":"glamorous-reunification-party","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/glamorous-reunification-party\/","title":{"rendered":"Glamorous Reunification Party"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47ka1tcc fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Rooftop-Party-for-Reunification-Day.jpg 1992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/3b30580b097d76c5444fdeaa002fbb07_Rooftop-Party-for-Reunification-Day-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/3b30580b097d76c5444fdeaa002fbb07_Rooftop-Party-for-Reunification-Day-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/3b30580b097d76c5444fdeaa002fbb07_Rooftop-Party-for-Reunification-Day-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/3b30580b097d76c5444fdeaa002fbb07_Rooftop-Party-for-Reunification-Day-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1992px) 100vw, 1992px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Rooftop-Party-for-Reunification-Day.jpg\" alt=\"Rooftop-Party-for-Reunification-Day\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-47lked41 fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-47lked42 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-47lked46 fg-image  img-responsive fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/ac20f3aebdec6c57e5010f109313569b_Logo-Events-on-26-gold-300-c-90.png\" alt=\"_Logo-Events-on-26-gold\"><div class=\"ffb-id-5daj6bqo ffg-empty-space fg-text-dark\"><\/div><h1 class=\"ffb-id-5daj2f7q fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center\">GLAMOROUS REUNIFICATION PARTY<\/h2>\n<p><\/h1><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-513fi7l5 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-47lked47 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Rooftop Party for Reunification Day!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Caravelle Saigon will host a Rooftop Party, on the Hotel Rooftop, to celebrate Reunification Day, and enjoy the best view for the Fireworks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">The Glamorous Reunification Party will be held on Saturday 30th April, from 5:00pm.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Enjoy Champagne and imported wines in a relaxing atmosphere, as you watch the Sun Set. The cool vibes of DJ Amora will accompany you though the evening, till the fireworks starts, from 9pm.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Sit back and chillout, in a panoramic views of the city&rsquo;s epic 15-minute fireworks, in the Heart of Saigon!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Diamonds: VND 7,900,000++<br \/>* Front stage sofa seating (up to 8 people)<br \/>* 2 Bottles of Champagne <br \/>* 2 set canapes<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Gold: VND 790,000++<br \/>* 1 bottle of Red wine<br \/>* Canape<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">Classic:<br \/>* Entrance fees VND 350,000++ per person<br \/>* Includes a glass of red or white wine<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">The Rooftop Party is adult only (minimum age 18 years-old)<br \/>Early Bird 10% off for reservation before April 28th<br \/>Book now: +84 2838 234 999<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-5jeuuds8 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>For more information please contact: (84) 2838 234 999 or email: culinary@caravellehotel.com<\/em><\/p